  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 97-9-115, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE CRIMINAL PENALTY FOR THE CRIME OF TAMPERING WITH A WITNESS TO BE A CERTAIN PERCENTAGE OF THE FINE AND IMPRISONMENT AUTHORIZED IN LAW FOR THE SUBJECT OFFENSE; TO DEFINE THE TERM \"SUBJECT OFFENSE\"; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
